y create dimension variations (16:9, 9:16, 1:1) and use <strong>Copy.ai</strong> to spin multiple ad copy descriptions.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Fast A/B testing is key; run your variations on a low budget to find the winning combination."}]'::jsonb
WHERE slug = 'ai-video-ad-creative-production';

UPDATE workflows
SET steps = '[{"goal":"Product Analysis & Hook Writing","step":1,"tools":[{"name":"ChatGPT","slug":"chatgpt"},{"name":"Claude AI","slug":"claude-ai"}],"description":"Research competitors and use <strong>ChatGPT</strong> or <strong>Claude AI</strong> to write compelling UGC hooks. Prompt: <em>''Write 5 TikTok UGC hooks for a skincare product that stop the scroll.''</em><br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Claude''s outputs often feel more native and less ''salesy'' for TikTok."},{"goal":"AI Avatar UGC Video Generation","step":2,"tools":[{"name":"HeyGen","slug":"heygen"},{"name":"Synthesia","slug":"synthesia"}],"description":"Use <strong>HeyGen</strong> or <strong>Synthesia</strong> to render realistic avatars delivering your UGC script in a casual, selfie-style format.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Choose an avatar holding a phone or standing in a living room background to make it feel like authentic user-generated content."},{"goal":"Video Editing & Caption Overlay","step":3,"tools":[{"name":"Descript","slug":"descript"},{"name":"Canva AI","slug":"canva"}],"description":"Edit in <strong>Descript</strong> or <strong>Canva AI</strong> to add trending stickers, bold native-looking captions, and rapid jump cuts.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Mimicking the native font of TikTok or Instagram Reels drastically improves watch time compared to highly polished corporate fonts."},{"goal":"Creative Variation & Scaling","step":4,"tools":[{"name":"InVideo AI","slug":"invideo-ai"},{"name":"Copy.ai","slug":"copy-ai"}],"description":"Use <strong>InVideo AI</strong> or <strong>Copy.ai</strong> to generate multiple voiceover variations (energetic vs. calm) for the exact same visual ad.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Even minor changes in audio tone can shift return on ad spend (ROAS). Test variations to see what the audience likes."}]'::jsonb
WHERE slug = 'ai-ugc-ad-creation';

UPDATE workflows
SET steps = '[{"goal":"Persuasive Copy & Headlines","step":1,"tools":[{"name":"ChatGPT","slug":"chatgpt"},{"name":"Jasper","slug":"jasper"}],"description":"Generate conversion-focused copy and headlines using <strong>Jasper</strong> or <strong>ChatGPT</strong>. Prompt: <em>''Write a landing page hero section targeting [audience] with a clear value proposition.''</em><br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Use the AIDA framework (Attention, Interest, Desire, Action)."},{"goal":"Hero Image & Visual Generation","step":2,"tools":[{"name":"Midjourney","slug":"midjourney"},{"name":"Adobe Firefly","slug":"adobe-firefly"}],"description":"Prompt <strong>Midjourney</strong> or <strong>Adobe Firefly</strong> for high-quality hero assets: <em>''3D isometric tech illustration, clean background, brand colors #0044cc''</em>.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Isolate the background using Canva AI to ensure your images blend perfectly into the webpage."},{"goal":"Page Design & Layout","step":3,"tools":[{"name":"Canva AI","slug":"canva"},{"name":"Beautiful.ai","slug":"beautiful-ai"}],"description":"Assemble the page mockups efficiently using <strong>Beautiful.ai</strong> or <strong>Canva</strong> UI templates.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Canva has thousands of pre-built landing page wireframes; simply replace the dummy text with your AI-generated copy and export the assets."},{"goal":"SEO & Copy Optimization","step":4,"tools":[{"name":"Surfer SEO","slug":"surfer-seo"},{"name":"Grammarly","slug":"grammarly"}],"description":"Optimize the final copy using <strong>Surfer SEO</strong> for organic search ranking and <strong>Grammarly</strong> for punchiness.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Make sure your call-to-action (CTA) button text is action-oriented (e.g., ''Start Building Free'' instead of just ''Submit'')."},{"goal":"Analytics & Conversion Tracking","step":5,"tools":[{"name":"n8n","slug":"n8n"},{"name":"Activepieces","slug":"activepieces"}],"description":"Use <strong>n8n</strong> or <strong>Activepieces</strong> to route form submissions directly to a Google Sheet and trigger auto-responder emails.<br><br>💡 <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Fast response times are vital. Set the n8n logic to ping a Slack channel instantly when a high-value lead submits a form."}]'::jsonb
WHERE slug = 'ai-landing-page-creation';

